data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This is a must see!!! Gorgeous immaculate 3 bedroom/2 bath Oviedo home located in the highly desirable Riverside at Twin Rivers Community. Walking in you'll notice how open and inviting this home is and how perfect it is for entertaining! Boasting a wonderful split floorplan, beautiful wood look tile floors throughout entire home and an abundance of natural light.   This beautiful home has been fully updated!  The upgraded kitchen includes custom made cabinets w/soft close drawers, Brazilian Granite counter tops, Stainless Steel appliances and Stainless Steel farm sink. Beautiful fenced in landscaped large backyard! The remodel was done in 2016 with lots of upgrades including newer hurricane windows on back of house as well as doors. Roof 2016, newer AC! Located in the highly sought after Seminole County school district. Walking distance to A Rated schools! Close to grocery stores, retail shopping and restaurants and only 30 minutes to the Orlando International Airport, 45 minutes to the attractions and 45 minutes to the beach. Book your showing today!
